data.description: This well-designed 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home was built in 2018 and is located in the desirable Sebastian Highlands neighborhood. The home has been meticulously maintained and is move-in ready. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining, while the split bedrooms provide great privacy. The screened porch is an ideal spot to relax and enjoy your favorite meal cooked on the barbecue. The spacious two-car garage provides ample room for your vehicles and extra storage. With its modern features and prime location, this home is sure to impress!
